{
  "page": "Axe (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b><a href=\"/index.php/Axe\" title=\"Axe\">Axe</a></b> is a peninsula on the northern coast of Essos.\n</p><p>You may be looking for:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Arson_Iceaxe\" title=\"Arson Iceaxe\">Arson Iceaxe</a>, a wilding raider.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ax_Isle\" title=\"Ax Isle\">Ax Isle</a>, an isle off the northern coast of Sothoryos.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Axel_Tully\" title=\"Axel Tully\">Axel Tully</a>, the first Lord of Riverrun.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Axell_Florent\" title=\"Axell Florent\">Axell Florent</a>, a knight of House Florent.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Durran_Durrandon_(Bronze-Axe)\" title=\"Durran Durrandon (Bronze-Axe)\">Durran Bronze-Axe</a>, a Storm King of House Durrandon.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gedmund_Peake\" title=\"Gedmund Peake\">Gedmund Peake</a>, a knight of House Peake known as \"Gedmund Great-Axe\".</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lorren_Longaxe\" title=\"Lorren Longaxe\">Lorren Longaxe</a>, a crew member on the <i>Black Wind</i>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mad_Axe\" title=\"Mad Axe\">Mad Axe</a>, a brother of the Night's Watch.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Qarl_Quickaxe\" title=\"Qarl Quickaxe\">Qarl Quickaxe</a>, an ironborn.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Silveraxe_Fell\" title=\"Silveraxe Fell\">Silveraxe Fell</a>, a member of House Fell during Robert's Rebellion.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Axe_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Armament#Axes\" title=\"Armament\">Armament</a>, for the weapon.\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260407111213\nCache ex